outputs.output_descr:
The project is focusing on:
1. Reconstruction of the destroyed infrastructure that led to the improvement of the level of basic social services for the target group;
2. Recovery of the foundations that support income generating activities and contribute to the recovery of livelihoods;
3. Capacity building of the civil society and local governments and involving them in the process of identifying intervention's priorities and the implementation of developmental projects;
4. Enhancing the preservation of the environment: towards integrated water and sold waste management, and an increase in the use of renewable energy;
5. Increasing income generation and employment opportunities, focusing on women and youth groups in the sectors of agriculture, agro-industries and small enterprises (shoe-making, pottery, glass industry, fishery, beekeeping, etc.);
6. Increasing youth participation in local development processes;
7. Improving the quality of education in public schools.
